@startuml state_machine

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced

title modbus_c -- RTU Slave State Machine

[*] --> INIT : power-on

INIT : Enter: reset rx/tx buffers\nstart 3.5t timer

IDLE : Waiting for first\ncharacter (SOF)

SOF : Start-of-Frame\ndetected\n1st byte buffered\nstart 1.5t timer

RECV : Receiving frame bytes\nreset 1.5t timer\non each byte

EOF : 1.5t elapsed --\npossible end of frame\nstart 3.5t timer

BUSY : Sending reply\nover serial

INIT --> IDLE : 3.5t silent\ninterval elapsed

IDLE --> SOF : byte received\n(serial_recv_cb)\nsuspend_cb()

SOF --> RECV : next byte received\n(serial_recv_cb)

RECV --> RECV : byte received\n(timer reset)

RECV --> EOF : 1.5t timer\nexpired

EOF --> IDLE : 3.5t confirmed\nCRC check\npdu_cb()\nreply -> BUSY or stay IDLE\nresume_cb()

IDLE --> BUSY : [reply ready]\nserial_send()

BUSY --> INIT : serial_sent_cb()\ntransmission complete

INIT --> INIT : error
SOF --> INIT : error
RECV --> INIT : error
EOF --> INIT : error
BUSY --> INIT : error

note right of EOF
  ADU validated:
  * minimum size >= 4 bytes
  * CRC-16 verified
  pdu_cb invoked with
  address, fcode, payload
end note

note right of BUSY
  Reply frame built by pdu_cb
  CRC appended automatically
end note

@enduml
